flowchart LR
    A[Start] --> B{claude installed?}

    B -->|No| C[Exit]
    B -->|Yes| D{Prompt exists?}

    D -->|No| C
    D -->|Yes| E{Git clean?}

    E -->|No| C
    E -->|Yes| F[Checkout MAIN_BRANCH]

    F --> G[Pull Latest]
    G --> H[Create Agent Branch]

    H --> I[Run Claude Agent]

    I --> J{.agent-stuck exists?}

    J -->|Yes| K[Show Reason]
    K --> L[Exit Failed]

    J -->|No| M{.agent-complete exists?}

    M -->|Yes| N[Show Complete]
    M -->|No| O[Show Finished]

    N --> P[Print Diff Summary]
    O --> P

    P --> Q[Done]
